<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EMA522_05_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css">

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema522_05_su.css">

</head>

<body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_05_su_0003">
        <section class="title type2">
            <h2 data-head="1_green" class="fraction_box_title">
                <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                    <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                        나은이는 3 ㎞를 걸으려고 하고, 하준이는 나은이가 걸으려고 하는 거리의
                        <span class="mixed_fraction">
                            <span>1</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span>1</span>
                                <span>4</span>
                            </span>
                        </span>
                        만큼을 걸으려고 합니다. 하준이가 걸으려고 하는
                    </div>
                    <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                        거리는 몇 ㎞인지 알아봅시다.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </h2>
        </section>

        <section class="contents paging_layout">
            <div class="input_area">
                <article class="page page_1">
                    <div class="img_row">

                        <div class="picture_wrap type2">
                            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA522_05_SU/0002_img01.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />
                            <div class="flex dir_col f24r">
                                <div class="mixed_fraction">
                                    <span>3 ㎞ 의 </span>
                                    <span class="mixed_fraction">
                                        <span>1</span>
                                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>4</span></span>
                                    </span>
                                    <span>만큼을</span>
                                </div>
                                <div>어떻게 구할 수 있을까?</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="input_area">
                            <h3 lang="y">구하는 식을 써 보세요.</h3>

                            <!-- 단답형 분수식 -->
                            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap flex align_center">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="3xx1(1)/(4)" text-align="center"
                                   ></math-field>
                                <!-- 분수식 ex) 15(1)/(2) -->
                                <!-- 매스필드 키패드 입력으로 분수 입력하는경우 정답 표기방법 -->
                                <!-- (분자)/(분모) 형식으로 표시 -->
                                <!-- xx, -:, ⋯ 는 수식 표시 형식으로 표시 각각 곱기호, 나눗셈기호, 중간점3개 -->
                                <!-- 힌트도 같은 형식으로 처리되서 나옴 -->
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_2">
                    <h3 lang="y">하준이가 걸으려고 하는 거리는 몇 ㎞인가요? 어림셈한 결과와 비교해 보세요.</h3>
                    <div class="input_area m_auto">
                        <div class="question_box">
                            <div class="mixed_fraction gap_8 m_auto">
                                <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="left">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="3" text-align="center"></math-field>
                                </div>
                                <span class="f32b" lang="y">㎞</span>
                                <span class="f32b" lang="y">로 어림할 수 있습니다.</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input_wrap mt_20">
                            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                            <ol class="example_box">
                                <li lang="y">
                                    <span class="mixed_fraction">
                                        3&times;1=3 (㎞) 이고 1<span
                                            class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>4</span></span>은
                                        1보다 조금 더 크기 때문입니다.
                                    </span>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="page page_3">
                    <h3 lang="y">
                        <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                                그림을 보고 3&times;1과
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>1</span>
                                    <span>4</span>
                                </span>
                                을 계산하는 방법을 알아보세요.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </h3>
                    <div class="question_box align_start dir_col">
                        <div class="tit">
                            <span class="label" lang="y"><i>방법1</i></span>
                            <span class="tit_txt" lang="y">대분수를 자연수와 진분수의 합으로 나타내어 계산하기​</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap_40">
                            <div class="reveal_wrap f24b">
                                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA522_05_SU/0003_img01.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />
                                <span class="abs_1" lang="y">3&times;1</span>
                                <span class="abs_2" lang="y"><span>0</span><span>3</span></span>
                                <span class="abs_3"
                                    lang="y"><span>0</span><span>1</span><span>2</span><span>3</span></span>
                                <span class="abs_4 f24b flex align_center" lang="y">
                                    <span>3&times;</span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box">
                                        <span>1</span>
                                        <span>4</span>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mixed_fraction f32b">
                                <span>3&times;1</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>1</span>
                                    <span>4</span>
                                </span>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <span class="group_box box_1">
                                    (3&times;1)
                                </span>
                                <span>+</span>
                                <span class="group_box box_2 ">
                                    <span class="mixed_fraction">
                                        (
                                        <span>3&times;</span>
                                        <span class="fraction_box">
                                            <span>1</span>
                                            <span>4</span>
                                        </span>
                                        )
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <span class="input_wrap">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                </span>
                                <span>+</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                    </span>
                                    <span>4</span>
                                </span>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <span class="input_wrap">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                </span>
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                    </span>
                                    <span>4</span>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_4">
                    <h3 lang="y">
                        <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                                그림을 보고 3&times;1과
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>1</span>
                                    <span>4</span>
                                </span>
                                을 계산하는 방법을 알아보세요.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </h3>
                    <div class="question_box align_start dir_col">
                        <div class="tit">
                            <span class="label" lang="y"><i>방법2</i></span>
                            <span class="tit_txt" lang="y">대분수를 가분수로 나타내어 계산하기​</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap_40">
                            <div class="reveal_wrap f24b">
                                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA522_05_SU/0003_img02.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />
                                <span class="abs_1 f24b flex align_center" lang="y">
                                    <span>3&times;</span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box">
                                        <span>1</span>
                                        <span>4</span>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                                <span class="abs_2"
                                    lang="y"><span>0</span><span>1</span><span>2</span><span>3</span><span>4</span></span>
                                <span class="abs_3 f24b flex align_center" lang="y">
                                    <span>3&times;</span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box">
                                        <span>5</span>
                                        <span>4</span>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mixed_fraction f32b">
                                <span>3&times;1</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>1</span>
                                    <span>4</span>
                                </span>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <span>3&times;</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field data-answer-single="5"></math-field>
                                    </span>
                                    <span>4</span>
                                </span>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>
                                        <span>3&times;</span>
                                        <span class="input_wrap">
                                            <math-field data-answer-single="5"></math-field>
                                        </span>
                                    </span>
                                    <span>4</span>
                                </span>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field data-answer-single="15"></math-field>
                                    </span>
                                    <span>4</span>
                                </span>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <span class="input_wrap">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                </span>
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                    </span>
                                    <span>4</span>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="page page_5 ">
                    <h3 lang="y">하준이가 걸으려고 하는 거리는 몇 km인가요? 어림셈한 결과와 비교해 보세요.</h3>
                    <div class="input_area m_auto">
                        <div class="question_box">
                            <div class="flex align_center gap_8 m_auto">
                                <!-- 단답형 분수식 -->
                                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap flex align_center" data-hint-position="left">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="3(3)/(4)" text-align="center"
                                       ></math-field>
                                    <!-- 분수식 ex) 15(1)/(2) -->
                                    <!-- 매스필드 키패드 입력으로 분수 입력하는경우 정답 표기방법 -->
                                    <!-- (분자)/(분모) 형식으로 표시 -->
                                    <!-- xx, -:, ⋯ 는 수식 표시 형식으로 표시 각각 곱기호, 나눗셈기호, 중간점3개 -->
                                    <!-- 힌트도 같은 형식으로 처리되서 나옴 -->
                                </div>
                                <span class="f32b" lang="y">㎞</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input_wrap mt_20">
                            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                            <div class="example_box">
                                <p lang="y">
                                    어림셈한 결과와 비슷합니다.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>


                <article class="page page_6">
                    <h3 lang="y">
                        (자연수)×(대분수)를 계산하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.
                    </h3>
                    <div class="input_area">
                        <div class="input_area m_auto">
                            <div class="input_wrap">
                                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                                <div class="example_box">
                                    <p>대분수를 자연수와 진분수의 합으로 나타내어 계산하거나 대분수를 가분수로 나타내어 계산합니다.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>

            <div class="btn_area">
                <!-- 예시 필드에서 사용 -->
                <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
                <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>                
                <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
                <button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true">제출</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>